Package: rdaemon
Type: Package
Title: run an R daemon process in the background
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2021-08-09
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jiefei",
           family = "Wang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "szwjf08@gmail.com")
Description: 
    Run an independent R daemon process in the background. The process will
    keep running even after its parent process quits. The other R sessions 
    can connect with the existing daemon using the daemon name and send 
    the task via 'daemonSetTask()'.
